{"tid":1702393,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「和理非」老豆搵仔 x 連儂牆「敵人清洗即係有用」","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:24:59.000Z","uid":38164,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad02295a2f4b50d286cfefaf0ab9e4eac29e0dd8","tid":1702393,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"和理非手足休息夠未？<br />\n呢排連儂牆俾人清得7788 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">是時候重建了</span></span><br />\n是時侯去返初期咁狂貼d黑警<br />\n<br />\n我地就用老豆搵仔既野貼上連儂牆<br />\n18區都貼滿佢<br />\n所有嘅暴行、威水史一覽無遺<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有成幾百個黑警資料貼，獲獲新鮮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，敵人清嘅速度越快<br />\n代表越有用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSprktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=c8e3b2da\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com/</a><br />\n藍屍也不例外<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"613c13c980ea8e32d854745a69c587b0372f7333","tid":1702393,"uid":259749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"b214a3e77541bab882166a5233909c0e900b2438","tid":1702393,"uid":38164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"流動式貼街招都可以<br />\n要令到佢哋精神打擊"},{"pid":"d1d1d6711c55e63a424cff6c9e312f0a0bba299e","tid":1702393,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561d8c170d134d0fab8ab98e589537ab01d290b2","tid":1702393,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":